q´eq t-xmakal. Kab´e xjal nya b´a´n ky-ka´yin n-chi ky-ka´yin ti´j toj
t-xlekumal jun ttzi ja, n-chi yolin kyxolx. N-chi tzalaj, a Harry tzaj tqona
b´et, n-chi jyon tu´n t-xi t-xo´n t-lente toj ttxolil extzen n-chi ayon ti´j q´uqb´il tk´u´j qa k-okil
b´a´n t-xi tkanet jun b´e tun t-xi´ya tzalu.
jun ojtxi´ t-xaq b´e b´incha´n twitz tze´ n-ok t-xmo´n tib´aj jun k´ayb´il n-k´ayin veneno
aye q´aq´ n-chi kyq´ama´n te qa at toj Knockturn Alley. A jlu mya onin, ikytzin b´ant tu´n Harry
mintiʼ o tzʼok nbʼiʼne jun lugar ik tzeʼn jlu. Kub´ t-ximin qa mya b´a´n t-yolin
