A q´oj te quidditch te amb´il, n-xi n-nimane? Gryffindor twitz Slytherin, atzun
mya? N-b´i´ne qa jun b´inchal b´itz teya. Ax ikx weye jun Seeker. tzaj q´ma´n weye tun n-xi n-b´inchene
