“exttzen aye ab´q´i otaq tzik´,” chi Aragog tuk´e t-xob´il. “Aqe ab´q´i extzen ab´q´i tzik´. Ayine
b´a´n t-ximana. Tuʼntzun jlu kubʼ kybʼinchaʼn tuʼn tetz toj tja xnaqʼtzbʼil. Aqe
