“Mya b´a´n tu´n t-xi n-najsa´ne til Hagrid. At q-suerte qu´n itz´qo.
“N-ximane qa n-ximana qa a Aragog mya n-chi b´inchan nya b´a´n kyi´j tamiw,” chi Harry.
